                            text="&lt;p>You can replace the current asset configuration in a subfolder by creating there another asset configuration. Only the properties of this configuration are used for image rendering of the containing images.&lt;/p>&lt;p>Example (in the prototype content)&lt;/p>&lt;p>/content/prototype/composum/assets/site-3/images/special&lt;/p>&lt;p>defines a new configuration and hides /content/prototype/composum/assets/site-3&lt;/p>"
